<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Harvest Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Famous for its picturesque lake, the Harvest Hills is a well planned residential neighborhood located in the northeast quadrant of Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given its central location within the city, the <span class="par-xl">Harvest Hills enjoys close proximity to a myriad of shopping centers and recreational venues including the Country Hills Towne Centre, TnT Asian Food Market, and the Cross Iron Mills complex</span>.</p>
